  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26001269_4_34506-34541",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "34506-34541",
      "markText": "即使在最亲密的朋友之间，奉承和赞扬也是需要的，就像车轮需要润滑油一样。",
      "totalCount": 1008,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26001269&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=34506&rangeEnd=34541",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9dc321b0718cbf759dc79a5?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=34506&rangeEnd=34541"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26001269_4_69204-69303",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "69204-69303",
      "markText": "德鲁别茨基公爵夫人抱住她，哭了。伯爵夫人也哭了。她们哭，因为她们是好朋友，因为她们心肠都很好，因为她们虽是老朋友，却不得不为金钱这种脏东西操心，还因为她们的青春一去不返……不过，两人都哭得很痛快……",
      "totalCount": 986,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26001269&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=69204&rangeEnd=69303",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9dc321b0718cbf759dc79a5?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=69204&rangeEnd=69303"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26001269_8_35148-35223",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "35148-35223",
      "markText": "安德烈公爵走进妻子屋里。她死了，像五分钟前他看见时那样躺着，她那张孩子般怯弱的美丽小脸上，上唇长着黑毫毛，虽然眼珠停滞不动，脸颊苍白，但表情并没有变。",
      "totalCount": 954,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26001269&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=35148&rangeEnd=35223",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9dc321b0718cbf759dc79a5?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=35148&rangeEnd=35223"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26001269_4_43387-43467",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "43387-43467",
      "markText": "他们三人不知从哪里弄来一头狗熊，坐马车把它带到女演员家里。警察跑去阻止。他们竟抓住警长，把他和狗熊背对背绑在一起，投到莫依卡河里；狗熊在河里游，背上还驮着警长。",
      "totalCount": 826,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26001269&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=43387&rangeEnd=43467",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9dc321b0718cbf759dc79a5?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=43387&rangeEnd=43467"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26001269_4_2346-2378",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2346-2378",
      "markText": "他像一只上足发条的时钟，习惯成自然地说着自己也不想叫人相信的话。",
      "totalCount": 799,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26001269&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2346&rangeEnd=2378",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9dc321b0718cbf759dc79a5?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2346&rangeEnd=2378"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26001269_16_1709-1766",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "1709-1766",
      "markText": "只有承认无穷小的单位——历史的微分（就是人的个人倾向）而进行观察，并掌握求积分的方法，我们才有希望认识历史的规律。",
      "totalCount": 792,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26001269&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=1709&rangeEnd=1766",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9dc321b0718cbf759dc79a5?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=1709&rangeEnd=1766"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26001269_16_23648-23671",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "23648-23671",
      "markText": "皮埃尔在路上听到了自己内弟和安德烈公爵的死讯。",
      "totalCount": 765,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26001269&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=23648&rangeEnd=23671",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9dc321b0718cbf759dc79a5?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=23648&rangeEnd=23671"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26001269_9_53396-53456",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "53396-53456",
      "markText": "尼古拉自从输钱以后，决定在五年内向父母还清这笔债。每年家里给他寄一万卢布，他决定今后只拿两千，其余八千留下来还父母的债。",
      "totalCount": 684,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26001269&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=53396&rangeEnd=53456",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9dc321b0718cbf759dc79a5?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=53396&rangeEnd=53456"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26001269_4_2768-2813",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2768-2813",
      "markText": "她好像一个被宠坏的孩子，明知自己有招人喜爱的缺点，却不愿也不能加以克服，甚至认为无须克服。",
      "totalCount": 680,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26001269&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2768&rangeEnd=2813",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9dc321b0718cbf759dc79a5?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2768&rangeEnd=2813"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26001269_4_121353-121365",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "121353-121365",
      "markText": "谁了解人，谁就能原谅人。",
      "totalCount": 666,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26001269&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=121353&rangeEnd=121365",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9dc321b0718cbf759dc79a5?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=121353&rangeEnd=121365"
    },
